        {
            "title": "3月新盤撻訂增7%至31宗  殺訂逾2100萬｜Seasons Place、維港滙III及曉柏峰列前三",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse內部統計顯示，2026年3月全港新盤共錄得31宗終止買賣合約（撻訂）個案，較2月的29宗增加2宗，按月上升約6.9%。按已披露成交紀錄估算，月內涉及沒收的訂金合共約2,135.1萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當中，以將軍澳日出康城Seasons Place、維港滙III及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"曉柏峰\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:曉柏峰;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/曉柏峰\">曉柏峰</a>的撻訂宗數最多，三個樓盤分別錄得7宗、6宗及4宗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"二月新盤全月錄29宗撻訂 總殺訂逾2000萬｜凱柏峰II佔過半續成重災區\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:二月新盤全月錄29宗撻訂 總殺訂逾2000萬｜凱柏峰II佔過半續成重災區;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3QcSK6z\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">二月新盤全月錄29宗撻訂 總殺訂逾2000萬｜凱柏峰II佔過半續成重災區</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"1月新盤錄87 宗撻訂 凱柏峰成重災區佔40宗\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:1月新盤錄87 宗撻訂 凱柏峰成重災區佔40宗;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/406HsCS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">1月新盤錄87 宗撻訂 凱柏峰成重災區佔40宗</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Seasons Place錄7宗撻訂 個別個案遭沒收逾74萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據成交紀錄冊，上述7宗Seasons Place有6宗來自第3A座，1宗來自第3B座。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-af49dd14-ebe6-3d1b-8150-c79127950d6e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這批買家多於2024年採用即供付款入市，其中3宗涉及較高金額訂金損失，分別為第3A座29樓B室、第3A座8樓C室及第3A座51樓D室。以第3A座29樓B室為例，原定成交價為746.3萬元，買家已支付樓價10%作訂金，終止交易後估計遭沒收約74.63萬元。其餘兩宗個案成交價分別為732.9萬元及666.9萬元，估計分別損失約73.29萬元及66.69萬元訂金。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇Seasons Place價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇Seasons Place價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/495jo78\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇Seasons Place價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>維港滙III錄6宗 曉柏峰錄4宗</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除Seasons Place外，維港滙III及曉柏峰分別錄得6宗及4宗撻訂，合共佔全月總數約32.23%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>維港滙III：1宗屬10%訂金個案</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">維港滙III當中有1宗較大額個案，涉及第1B座9樓E室，原定成交價為706.49萬元。買家支付10%訂金後終止交易，估計遭沒收約70.64萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其餘5宗個案的買家則支付5%訂金，最終合共被沒收約186.96萬元，以每宗計算，涉及金額約35.5萬元至38.52萬元不等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇維港滙III價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇維港滙III價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3PSqohR\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇維港滙III價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>曉柏峰：1宗遭沒收逾96萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">曉柏峰方面，有1宗較大額個案涉及第B座20樓B4室，原定成交價為962.43萬元。買家支付10%訂金後放棄交易，估計遭沒收約96.24萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其餘3宗個案則屬支付5%訂金後終止交易，合共涉及沒收訂金約155.35萬元，每宗約45.45萬元至55.02萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇曉柏峰價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇曉柏峰價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4qAB15U\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇曉柏峰價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>柏瓏II、Park Seasons各錄3宗</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，柏瓏II及Park Seasons各錄得3宗撻訂，合共佔全月總數約19.35%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>柏瓏II 3宗均屬高價單位</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">柏瓏II的3宗撻訂個案，全部位於第9座A1室，分別為16樓、11樓及6樓單位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中，第9座16樓A1室原定成交價最高，作價1,904.05萬元，買家支付10%訂金後終止交易，估計損失約190.4萬元。其餘兩宗成交價分別為1,866.48萬元及1,836.91萬元，估計分別遭沒收約186.64萬元及183.69萬元訂金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇柏瓏II價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇柏瓏II價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47Segmp\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇柏瓏II價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Park Seasons有個案沒收逾82萬元</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Park Seasons方面，第2座（2B）28樓A室原以825.9萬元售出，買家選用「360天現金優惠付款計劃」，並支付10%訂金，最終終止交易，估計損失約82.59萬元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇Park Seasons價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇Park Seasons價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/485RYif\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇Park Seasons價單】</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>黃金海灣意嵐錄零星個案</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於其餘撻訂個案，則較為分散，其中黃金海灣意嵐錄得2宗，約佔全月總數6.45%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"【即睇黃金海灣意嵐價單】\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇黃金海灣意嵐價單】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3PVfQyt\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇黃金海灣意嵐價單】</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Kaqe5u8wdjTb56xSFC8lDg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/074c95a2b5973b89834dddb76033b361\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>圖一：2026年3月新盤撻訂記錄</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"曉柏峰\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:曉柏峰;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/曉柏峰\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">曉柏峰</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"黃金海灣意嵐\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:黃金海灣意嵐;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/new-properties/黃金海灣意嵐\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">黃金海灣意嵐</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Park Seasons\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:Park Seasons;elm:context_link;